#### BOSH CLI v2: Selecting a BOSH deployment

1. Retrieve the GUID of your service instance with command `cf service YOUR-SERVICE-INSTANCE --guid`.

1. To download your BOSH manifest for the service, run `bosh download manifest service-instance_SERVICE-INSTANCE-GUID myservice.yml` GUID you just obtained and a filename you want to save the manifest as.


#### BOSH CLI v1: Selecting a BOSH deployment

1. Retrieve the GUID of your service instance with command `cf service YOUR-SERVICE-INSTANCE --guid`.

1. To download your BOSH manifest for the service, run `bosh manifest service-instance_SERVICE-INSTANCE-GUID myservice.yml` GUID you just obtained and a filename you want to save the manifest as.

1. Run `bosh deployment MY-SERVICE.yml to select the deployment`.
